645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17044,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/sahabah-ten-ayat-ilm-amal\/","url_meta":{"origin":10959,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Companions learn ten verses at a time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Abdur Rahman reported: The companions would learn to recite ten verses from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. They would not take another ten verses until they understood the knowledge and deeds they contained. They would say, \"We learned sacred knowledge and action together.\" Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29237,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/12\/parents-hafiz-quran-crown\/","url_meta":{"origin":10959,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Parents of children who recite Quran given a crown","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh al-Juhani reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites the Quran and acts according to what is in it, his parents will be crowned on the Day of Resurrection with a light brighter than the light of the sun in your worldly houses,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27667,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/17\/quran-teach-comprehensive-surat\/","url_meta":{"origin":10959,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Teach me to recite a comprehensive Surah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessing be upon him, and he said, \u201cTeach me to recite, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cRecite three chapters which begin with Alif Lam Ra.\u201d The man said, \u201cI am very old. It will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35858,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/27\/surat-al-fatihah-unique\/","url_meta":{"origin":10959,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Surat al-Fatihah unlike any revealed scripture","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cHow do you recite in prayer?\u201d Ubayy said, \u201cI recite the foundation of the Book, Surat al-Fatihah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, nothing like it has\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"class